System Message:
        Access to the Oculus system has been granted by the Transpiral Treaty,
    only those parties who have signed the treaty are permitted to be within
    this system. Transit, trade and exploration may be carried out in these
    systems in accordance with DTR Law. All exploration results (including GPI
    results) must be shared with the DTR. Permits to build starbases, outposts
    and platforms must be granted by the DTR prior to building.

    Full laws of the DTR can be found at Library -> General -> Laws -> Factions
    -> Detinus Republic
